Package: odds.n.ends
Title: Computes Logistic Regression Model Fit, Model Significance, Odds Ratios
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Jenine Harris <harrisj@wustl.edu>
Maintainer: Jenine Harris <harrisj@wustl.edu>
Description: Computes and displays model significance, model fit, and odds ratios with 95 percent confidence intervals for a logistic regression object estimated using the generalized linear models package.
